<topic id="editing-perspectives">
  <title>Perspectives</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>Perspectives</indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p>An <ph keyref="product"/>
      <xref keyref="glossentry_perspective"><term>perspective</term></xref> is an interface layout
      geared towards a specific use. The <ph keyref="product"/> interface uses standard interface
      conventions and components to provide a familiar and intuitive editing environment across all
      operating systems. There are several <term>perspectives</term> that you can use to work with
      documents in <ph keyref="product"/>. You can change the <term>perspective</term> by selecting
      the respective icon <ph product="editor">(<image href="../img/Editor18.png"
          id="image_zdf_kpv_nkb"/><image href="../img/DITA18.png" id="image_qqy_lpv_nkb"/><image
          href="../img/Debugger18.png" id="image_hr2_npv_nkb"/><image
          href="../img/DebuggerXQuery18.png" id="image_nf1_4pv_nkb"/><image
          href="../img/Database18.png" id="image_xfr_4pv_nkb"/>)</ph><ph product="author">(<image
          href="../img/Editor18.png" id="image_d13_rpv_nkb"/><image href="../img/DITA18.png"
          id="image_e13_rpv_nkb"/><image href="../img/Database18.png" id="image_h13_rpv_nkb"
        />)</ph><ph product="developer">(<image href="../img/Editor18.png" id="image_ej3_q1g_4kb"
          /><image href="../img/Debugger18.png" id="image_gj3_q1g_4kb"/><image
          href="../img/DebuggerXQuery18.png" id="image_hj3_q1g_4kb"/><image
          href="../img/Database18.png" id="image_ij3_q1g_4kb"/>)</ph> in the top-right corner of <ph
        keyref="product"/> or by selecting the <term>perspective</term> from the <menucascade
        product="author developer editor">
        <uicontrol>Window</uicontrol>
        <uicontrol>Open Perspective</uicontrol>
      </menucascade><menucascade product="authorEclipse developerEclipse editorEclipse">
        <uicontrol>Window</uicontrol>
        <uicontrol>Perspective</uicontrol>
        <uicontrol>Open Perspective</uicontrol>
      </menucascade> menu.</p>
  </body>
